- Types: feat, fix, docs, refactor, test, chore
- Max 72 characters in subject line

### Hooks Installed
Run `dotconfigs project .` to install, or manually:
`cp ~/.dotconfigs/git-hooks/{pre-commit,commit-msg,pre-push} .git/hooks/ && chmod +x .git/hooks/*`
- **Pre-commit**: Identity check always, Ruff format on main only
- **Commit-msg**: Blocks AI attribution
- **Pre-push**: Tests + lint + type check

